TRECQuestion
          A TRECQuestion is a simple data structure consisting of a question ID, a question type, a question string and the answers returned by the QA engine.
TRECTarget
          A TRECTarget is a simple data structure consisting of the ID of the target, the target description, possible target types and a list of questions.
